Package fitnessclub

Class Date

java.lang.Object
fitnessclub.Date
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Date>
public class Date extends Object implements Comparable<Date>
Represents a date with the day, month, and year This class is uses a date input by the user to determine if the date is valid based on the boundaries. this class is also used to compare dates and return which comes before or after.
Author:
Joon Song, Connor Powell
